ASEPTIC MENINGITIS - MEXICO (02): (DURANGO) FATAL, FUNGAL, NOSOCOMIAL, POST-EPIDURAL ADMINISTRATION, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
****************************************************************************************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

[1]
Date: Sat 12 Nov 2022
Source: Excelsior [in Spanish, machine trans., edited]
https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/muere-otra-mujer-en-durango-por-meningitis-suman-4-decesos/1552023


The Durango Health Secretariat confirmed this Saturday [12 Nov 2022] the death of a woman from aseptic meningitis due to fungus, the 4th death from this condition.

The state agency stressed that the victim had a gynecologic and obstetric procedure carried out in a private hospital.

With this unfortunate death, 4 people have died due to this disease, which is why care is already provided to relatives through comprehensive assistance and supplies.

The Ministry of Health reported as of the end of Saturday [12 Nov 2022] there are no new cases of aseptic meningitis due to fungus and 42 cases remain.

The General Hospital 450, as well as those of ISSSTE [Mexican Institute for Social Security and Services for State Workers] and IMSS [Mexican Social Security Institute], follow the same protocol and the necessary medical infrastructure to provide immediate care in the event of any suspicion of this condition.

[Byline: Alma Gudiño]

